1
00:00:45,080 --> 00:00:47,540
Are you going to run away again in the future?

2
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,760
No, I won't.

3
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:53,480
I've decided to stay here and find out who the real culprit is.

4
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:54,520
Real culprit?

5
00:00:55,040 --> 00:00:55,880
That's right.

6
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:59,700
The murderer who killed my birth parents is in the Liu mansion.

7
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:04,080
I am the daughter of Jiang Huai, the head chef at Fulu Restaurant,

8
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:06,920
and Lingwu, the personal maid of Old Lady Liu.

9
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,000
When I was little,

10
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:12,080
they were brutally murdered.

11
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,760
But it's okay.

12
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,000
Now finally some clues are about to surface.

13
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,520
Look at this.

14
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:43,320
Yiyu, I found it.

15
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,920
I asked the elders at the market.

16
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:46,820
Five years ago,

17
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:49,039
Master Liu gathered the most famous craftsmen in the city,

18
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,840
selected a fine piece of Hetian jade,

19
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:53,720
and crafted this unique jade pendant for the young master.

20
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,400
It was his 18th birthday gift.

21
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:01,320
The young master?

22
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,800
Yes.

23
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:07,160
They say the young master's birth mother, Lady Liu, was extraordinarily beautiful in her lifetime

24
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,280
and shared a deep love with Master Liu.

25
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:12,440
That's why Master Liu was especially doting on the young master.

26
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,770
The whole city knows it.

27
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:17,800
I'm afraid it was the master's excessive indulgence

28
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,040
that made the young master arrogant and overbearing.

29
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,800
Until he caused trouble.

30
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:31,040
Husband, you've been ignoring me for days.

31
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,600
Have you grown tired of me?

32
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:37,760
Who was it that desperately insisted on bringing me into this household?

33
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,040
Don't you hate me?

34
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:41,280
Isn't this what you wanted?

35
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,680
Husband.

36
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:48,770
We've been married for days but haven't consummated our marriage.

37
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,680
Today is such a beautiful day, perhaps we could...

38
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,680
Husband, I've come to my senses.

39
00:02:58,200 --> 00:03:00,120
The Liu family is wealthy and powerful.

40
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,760
You are the eldest son.

41
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:05,040
A wise man knows when to adapt to circumstances.

42
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:08,400
Liu Sinan is merely a husband in name only.

43
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,120
Being your wife,

44
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,600
is my greatest fortune in three lifetimes.

45
00:03:13,040 --> 00:03:15,240
I was too immature before.

46
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:19,600
Please don't hold it against me.

47
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,300
