72
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,960
Quickly, go fetch a doctor.

73
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,480
Yes, Madam.

74
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:54,760
Yiyu.

75
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,040
Sinan.

76
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,880
Here's the slow-acting poison you asked me to find.

77
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,610
What are you going to use it for?

78
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:11,050
I've found the murderer who killed my birth parents.

79
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,720
Who?

80
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,280
It's Liu Silin.

81
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,760
How is that possible?

82
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:20,240
Although my brother mistreats and abuses his servants,

83
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,960
but at least he has...

84
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,560
Stop making excuses for him.

85
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,160
I know blood is thicker than water,

86
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,680
but I've confirmed it.

87
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,120
He's the one who murdered my birth parents.

88
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,680
Will you help me?

89
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,159
Since my brother has done such a thing,

90
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,530
his crime is unforgivable.

91
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,560
However, Yiyu,

92
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,040
what concerns me most

93
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,720
is your safety.

94
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,480
Hey, what's going on?

95
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,880
There was a fire in the young master's room yesterday.

96
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:03,880
The young master was frightened.

97
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,810
He's had a high fever all day today.

98
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,120
The master is furious.

99
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:09,320
He says if anything happens to the young master,

100
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,960
we'll all pay with our lives.

101
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,010
I'll go check on him.

102
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,600
The young mistress is back.

103
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,560
You may go now. I'll take care of him.

104
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,440
Yes.

105
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,680
Why is your hand so hot?

106
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,920
Take your medicine quickly.

107
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,880
Get Liu Silin out here.

108
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:25,720
Gentlemen, let's talk this through.

109
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,400
No need for weapons.

110
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,600
Hurry up and bring that crazy son out.

111
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:32,280
Or I won't be so polite anymore.

112
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,940
What's that sound?

113
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,560
Sounds like gunshots.

114
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:50,440
What are you doing?

115
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,880
I'm not dead yet.

116
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:07,000
What's going on here?

117
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:11,000
Young master, you absolutely cannot go out.

118
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,760
Why not?

119
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,720
The police are looking for you everywhere.

120
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:15,000
The master is furious right now.

121
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,600
If you go out now, you'll be in serious trouble.

122
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,880
Mr. Liu.

123
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,480
Excuse me.

124
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,410
I apologize for the intrusion.

125
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:28,740
Someone reported that

126
