127
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,559
I'm here under orders to arrest him.

128
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:38,240
Mr. Liu, we understand.

129
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,720
You're a big name in Yuncheng,

130
